---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Archive"
  description="Historical note on preserved Chinese SCSDA website materials and future archive publication."
>
  <section class="section">
    <div class="shell article narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Historical Archive</p>
      <h2>Earlier Chinese website materials are preserved as institutional records.</h2>
      <p>
        The previous Chinese SCSDA website has been preserved locally for
        reference, migration, and future archive publication. Its pages, images,
        videos, and documents remain useful source material for understanding
        the Academy's earlier public activities.
      </p>
      <p>
        The current English website presents a revised institutional profile,
        while selected historical pages can be curated separately as a public
        archive of earlier Academy activities.
      </p>
      <div class="callout">
        Future plan: publish selected historical materials under a clearly
        labelled archive path after file review, link repair, and content
        screening.
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
